    <sec disp-level="1" id="ltxid3" specific-use="section">
      <label>1</label>
      <title>one</title>
      <p>
        <disp-formula content-type="math/tex">
          <tex-math>\begin{equation}
 e = mc^2 \tag{EQ1}\cssId{EQ}{}
\end{equation}</tex-math>
        </disp-formula>
      </p>
      <p>
        <monospace>multline</monospace> is odd in that there can only be one equation tag. If you specify a custom <monospace>tag</monospace>, it can go on any line, but the tag still gets moved to the top (for leqno) or bottom (for reqno) lines.</p>
      <p>
        <monospace>texml</monospace> will move all <monospace>tag</monospace>s to the last line.</p>
      <p>
        <disp-formula content-type="math/tex">
          <tex-math>\begin{multline}
 XXX\\
YYY\\
ZZZ \tag{a}
\end{multline}</tex-math>
        </disp-formula>
      </p>
      <p>
        <disp-formula content-type="math/tex">
          <tex-math>\begin{multline}
 XXX\\
YYY\\
ZZZ \tag{b}
\end{multline}</tex-math>
        </disp-formula>
      </p>
      <p>
        <disp-formula content-type="math/tex">
          <tex-math>\begin{multline}
 XXX\\
YYY\\
ZZZ \tag{c}\cssId{YYY}{}
\end{multline}</tex-math>
        </disp-formula>
      </p>
      <p>EQ <x>(</x><xref ref-type="disp-formula" rid="EQ" specific-use="ref">EQ1</xref><x>)</x></p>
      <p>YYY <x>(</x><xref ref-type="disp-formula" rid="YYY" specific-use="ref">c</xref><x>)</x></p>
